snippet.title: Thorn for the Villain~ Reincarnated as an Extra in an Otome Game?! [DEMO RELEASE TRAILER]
snippet.description:
Download Link: https://ant-san.itch.io/villainotome

"Thorn for the Villain~ Reincarnated as an Extra in an Otome Game?!" is an otome isekai otome game inspired by otome isekai manhwas, webtoons, LNs, and manga.

Music: Hoshi ga Kaerutoki (Dova Syndrome/Flehmann)
SFX: Zapsplat
